;&#10;Tiredness:&#10;After each crime committing attempt, you have to wait for a &#10;predefined period in order to commit the same type of crime.&#10;&#10;FBI Raid Chance:&#10;Each crime has a specific FBI raid chance, that alters the&#10;total raid chance. FBI raid may result in jail time or money &#10;loss. Laundered money will be used after a loss.&#10;&#10;Upgrades: &#10;You can buy upgrades by clicking the &quot;Upgrades&quot; label&#10;on the main screen. A submenu appears on the right of the &#10;screen providing the options at different prices and ranks.&#10;You can get them for increasing your production rate, &#10;lowering raid chance etc.&#10;&#10;Game Over:&#10;Game ends when all of the health of the player is used up or &#10;when the player ends up in jail for 20 times.&#10;&#10;You're all set! Good luck in becoming a gangsta!&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;" />
